This project implements factors like hashing, collision handeling, and resizing.

Java Files:
HashMap.java - Implements hash table system. Uses put, get, remove, and handles collisions.
Node.java - Stores a key and value. Chains collsions in linked list.
HashingMetrics - Tracks performance stats by counting collisions, counting resizes, and measures execution time.
HashDataGenerator - Creates test data.
HashingMain - driver that creates dataset usuing DataGenerator, runs HashMap operations, tracks performance with HashingMetrics. 
